metadata.name: Temptation
metadata.description:
Kylie did well in school, then went to her first year of university, studied for two years and took a wrong turn, or maybe she didnâ€™t, everyone chooses their own path.
When she moved away from her parents, she went nuts. A new world opened up to her, a world of temptation. Drugs, sex, love, total freedom, and so on. She doesn't remember her old self anymore.
